milestones.description: Jonty Jenner and Asa Tribe's 34-run partnership is JER's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 30 between Jonty Jenner and Benjamin Ward
Benjamin Ward and Asa Tribe's 97-run partnership is JER's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 5 between Jonty Jenner and Sumerauer
Benjamin Ward and Sumerauer's 20-run partnership is JER's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 9 between Anthony Hawkins-Kay and Jake Dunford
Perchard and Elliot Miles's 6-run partnership is JER's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 1 between Perchard and Elliot Miles
Monank Patel has broken the record for most ducks (6) in ODIs for USA, going past Steven Taylor's 5
Steven Taylor has broken the record for most sixes (27) in ODIs for USA, going past Aaron Jones's 26
Asa Tribe has broken the record for most sixes (4) in ODIs for JER, going past Greenwood's 2
Netravalkar has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (43) for USA, going past Monank Patel
Carlyon has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (4) for JER, going past Jake Dunford
